DB2,演習問題解答

conn system
orcl
↑でログイン

62P
GRANT CREATE SESSION,CREATE TABLE,CREATE VIEW,CREATE SEQUENCE,CREATE SYNONYM,CREATE PUBLIC SYNONYM
TO TBOWNER;

65P
1.GRANT INSERT,DELETE,UPADTE,SELECT
ON SCOTT.emp
TO OPERATOR;

2.
GRANT SELECT
ON SCOTT.emp
TO SELECTOR;

↓conn SELECTER 
SELECTERPASSでログインしてこのクエリーが通らなければ正解
INSERT INTO scott.emp
(empno,ename)
VALUES(1,'aaa');


67P
CREATE ROLE OWNER;

GRANT CREATE SESSION, CREATE TABLE, CREATE VIEW, CREATE SEQUENCE, CREATE SYNONYM
TO OWNER;

CREATE ROLE DMLUSER;

GRANT CREATE SESSION
TO DMLUSER;

CREATE ROLE SELECTUSER;
GRANT CREATE SESSION
TO SELECTUSER;